BI Publisher Scheduler VS ESS Scheduler
Scenario	Recommended Option
Just want to test or email a report occasionally	BI Publisher Scheduler
Want a Fusion-wide scheduled process, visible to users	ESS Scheduler
Need to trigger report from SOAP/REST API or integration	ESS Scheduler
Need parameters with LOVs and roles	ESS Scheduler
Internal or one-time testing	BI Scheduler is fine
ğŸ Summary

In short:
BI Publisher Scheduler = personal, limited, standalone timer.
ESS Scheduler = enterprise-grade, role-based, monitored job engine across all Fusion modules.







